<h2 id="supported-command-lines" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#supported-command-lines"><span>Supported Command Lines</span></a></h2>
<p><code v-pre>npmTo</code> does not support all <code v-pre>npm</code> command lines. Here is the list of supported commands:</p>
<ul>
<li><code v-pre>npm install</code> / <code v-pre>npm i</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>npm run</code> / <code v-pre>npm run-script</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>npm init</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>npm create</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>npm uninstall</code> / <code v-pre>npm rm</code> / <code v-pre>npm remove</code> / <code v-pre>npm un</code> / <code v-pre>npm unlink</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>npm ci</code></li>
<li><code v-pre>npx</code></li>
</ul>
<div class="hint-container info">
<p class="hint-container-title">Info</p>
<p>For unsupported command lines, <code v-pre>npmTo</code> will not process them and will only copy them to the other code blocks.</p>
</div>
